1
00:00:40,119 --> 00:00:41,679
This is vigilante justice.

2
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:43,240
It's illegal, you know that?

3
00:00:43,399 --> 00:00:44,960
Tell me, massaging you like this,

4
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:46,000
could I make a living?

5
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:46,719
Of course you can.

6
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:49,439
Then just sign the Aimin Street contract.

7
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:51,320
Turn the layoffs into transfers.

8
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:52,600
The leftover money,

9
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:54,280
wouldn't that all be our factory's profit?

10
00:00:54,799 --> 00:00:55,280
Sign your name.

11
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:55,520
Sign your name.

12
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:55,880
Sign it!

13
00:00:56,119 --> 00:00:57,359
Fine, I'll sign.

14
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:07,120
Boss Long, who am I?

15
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:10,439
What?

16
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,200
I said, who am I?

17
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,079
Secretary Yu.

18
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,799
Let's not joke around, okay?

19
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,439
Which real estate company in all of Night City

20
00:01:19,439 --> 00:01:20,480
doesn't know who you are?

21
00:01:21,599 --> 00:01:22,719
So do you

22
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:24,040
think I'm easy to fool?

23
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:25,519
Secretary Yu, this...

24
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:26,560
What does fifty-two mean?

25
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:30,159
This fifty-two...

26
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,760
I suspect it's Ge Zhendong and that...

27
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,560
Boss Long.

28
00:01:34,439 --> 00:01:35,599
Our previous cooperation

29
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:36,480
has gone pretty smoothly.

30
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,879
But this Aimin Street project

31
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,680
is more important than all the others.

32
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:41,640
If anything goes wrong with Aimin Street,

33
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,640
I think Night City

34
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,239
doesn't necessarily need the Giant Wood Group.

35
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,040
What do you think?

36
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,319
You're absolutely right.

37
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:47,959
Secretary Yu,

38
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:50,760
don't disappoint me again.

39
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:53,480
Zhu Yihai,

40
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:57,840
If you're heartless, don't blame me for being ruthless.

41
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,000
Excuse me,

42
00:02:13,479 --> 00:02:15,400
is Mr. Zhu Yihai here?

43
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,000
Mr. Zhu?

44
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,360
We do have a Brother Zhu here.

45
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,159
What for?

46
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:31,120
Brother Zhu helped me the other day.

47
00:02:31,439 --> 00:02:32,919
I came specifically to thank him.

48
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:33,759
No need.

49
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,120
How do you plan on thanking me?

50
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,159
Brother Zhu,

51
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:54,960
will you teach me to play pool?

52
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:56,319
No way.

53
00:02:59,199 --> 00:03:00,120
I can.

54
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:03,120
Just playing is too boring.

55
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,840
How about we add a little sweetener?

56
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:08,120
What kind of sweetener?

57
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:10,639
Whoever wins between us

58
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,199
has to do one thing for the other.

59
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:15,840
How about it?

60
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,240
But I'd like to think you're a good kid.

61
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:24,159
Good kids shouldn't have bad intentions.

62
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,520
Hey,

63
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:30,800
you two,

64
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,120
Get a room!

65
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:35,000
What if I do have bad intentions?

66
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,560
Hey, Zhu Yihai,

67
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,719
what are you doing here?

68
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,400
Don't be mad, don't be mad.

69
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,560
How can I not be mad?

70
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:41,960
Getting handsy with someone.

71
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,960
I said he wouldn't do that.

72
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:49,879
I didn't bump into you, did I?

73
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:31,399
I didn't touch her.

74
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:32,800
She twisted it.

75
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,600
Sprained her ankle.

76
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:42,000
If you know, why ask?

77
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:45,959
Quick.

78
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,120
Rub it for me.

79
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:58,399
Done playing? Move it.

80
00:04:58,399 --> 00:04:59,319
Others need the table.

81
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,800
Can you slow down?

82
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,759
She's injured, you know.

83
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:08,040
Forget it, forget it.

84
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,279
So many people in this pool hall.

85
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,399
People get jealous easily.

86
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:18,399
Didn't know that besides being handsome,

87
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,120
you also know how to care for someone.

88
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:23,040
You won the game.

89
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,639
So tell me, what do you want?

90
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,160
Don't be so serious.

91
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:29,720
I won't bite.

92
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,079
You're shameless.

93
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:32,839
Alright, I'll make my request then.

94
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,000
Don't back out.

95
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:38,839
Only dogs back out.

96
00:05:42,079 --> 00:05:43,680
I want you to sing Karaoke with me.

97
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,360
Karaoke?

98
00:05:45,759 --> 00:05:46,879
Sure.

99
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,839
Put on the fur coat.

100
00:05:56,439 --> 00:05:57,519
Money's right here.

101
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:05,600
I can't stand Zhu Yihai's stupid face.

102
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,680
Hasn't Dahai always been like that?

103
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,920
Look at how you were acting.

104
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,240
I just don't want him to end up

105
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,839
like Dali's dad, you know?

106
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,040
Dali.

107
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:18,399
I didn't mean it that way.

108
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:19,480
Don't get me wrong.

109
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,360
Don't take it to heart.

110
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,360
You're right.

111
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,600
He's gone astray.

112
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,839
I gotta have a word with that woman.

113
00:06:28,519 --> 00:06:29,040
Dali.

114
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,279
Dali.

115
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,160
Dali.

116
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:40,000
We're like a dotted line,

117
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:47,519
fading in and out in the monsoon.

118
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,160
So then,

119
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,360
what are you waiting for?

120
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:06,839
Why are you so naughty?

121
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:09,000
Could I ever be as bad as you?

122
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,600
I just don't get it.

123
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:12,399
Get what?

124
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:15,879
I don't get why you came looking for me.

125
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,399
Do you believe in fate?

126
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:21,279
I believe in orders.

127
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:24,240
What do you mean?

128
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:29,199
You wouldn't be here without a reason.

129
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,680
What are you really after?

130
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,399
Brother Hai.

131
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:34,480
Brother Hai.

132
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,040
Qianmei.

133
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,879
What are you doing here?

134
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:38,519
They...

135
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:40,519
They want to drag me off as a hostess.

136
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,560
Brother Hai.

137
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:45,800
Brother Hai.

138
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,040
Stay out of this.

139
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,600
This woman owes us money.

140
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,959
Hurry up.

141
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,920
Brother Hai, save me.

142
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:52,680
Move.

143
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,199
What are you doing?

144
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,160
You really getting involved?

145
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,560
Of course I am.

146
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,879
Brother Hai.

147
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:01,279
You're putting us in a tough spot.

148
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:02,560
I'm just doing my job.

149
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,399
Come on, brother, lighten up.

150
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,519
Tell you what.

151
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,399
Let her keep me company tonight.

152
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,000
After that,

153
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:10,040
I'll bring her over tomorrow, deal?

154
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:15,199
Brother Hai's a person of sentiment too.

155
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:16,839
Fine.

156
00:08:16,839 --> 00:08:18,839
Wishing Brother Hai a night of passion.

157
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,639
All night long.

158
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:24,319
Thank you.

159
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:25,600
Thanks, brother.

160
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,360
Alright.

161
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,480
Hurry home.

162
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,399
Go on.

163
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,560
Go, go, go.

164
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,720
What are you looking at?

165
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:40,679
What are you looking at?

166
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,600
Are we drinking or what?

167
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,399
Let's drink.

168
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,480
No matter what tonight,

169
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:50,279
I'm having a drink with the big hero.

170
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,159
Drink this.

171
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,360
What are you thinking about?

172
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:12,559
I'm wondering...

173
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:14,840
who could've sent you.

174
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:24,080
Room 302 has the answer you want.

175
00:10:04,799 --> 00:10:05,799
The money's right here.

176
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,840
Alright.

177
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,840
Sly as a fox.

178
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,799
If I weren't sharp,

179
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:20,159
I'd actually think you fell for me.

180
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:21,759
Just you wait.

181
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:24,039
As for the rest,

182
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:25,279
watch me work my magic.

183
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:37,879
My dear Jiao Jing,

184
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,679
tonight I come to your door.

185
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:42,799
Will you open it for me?

186
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,600
Who is it?

187
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,080
Jingjing.

188
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,039
Jingjing.

189
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,879
Coming, coming.

190
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:01,519
Jingjing.

191
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:05,120
Didn't I give you a key?

192
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:07,919
What's the rush?
